// ...
```
This is the call! It's around line 2060. And there is no `SrcVTy` in scope here. The variable `SrcVTy` is defined much earlier, but it might not be what I think it is.
```cpp
// ...
  VectorType *SrcVTy = cast<VectorType>(V1->getType());
  unsigned DstEltCnt = DstVecTy->getNumElements();
  if (SrcVTy->getNumElements() != DstEltCnt)
